{
  "stem": "14060.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All I would like to say is that we were very much aware what was happening.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we read the newspapers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We used to listen to the BBC.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father understood a bit of English, and even others did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was highly dangerous because that was a criminal offense.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Once the Germans came in, it was basically-- Jews were, I don't think, allowed to use radios.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They came in on the 19th of March.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were at home still on Pesach.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I think I looked up the dates with you in a 100 year calendar recently.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were taken out of the ghetto into the half-built brick factory on the 29th of June.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We must have been in the ghetto approximately five, or six, or maybe seven weeks maximum, which was in the-- there were two ghettos in town.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "One was near where the orthodox shul was, which was a high wooden fence, and people were stopped to get in or out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the other one was in the center of town, which is a very old part of it and called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So one street just with two houses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That is the one which we were in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That is where I mentioned that in the Communist time they discovered the medieval old synagogue, which dates back from year 1100 or before.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were taken out of a very comfortable home into given a room with my parents and my brother and myself with meager belongings and doing nothing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But we were taken out-- anybody who was of working age, or who could volunteer-- to do agricultural work in the nearby fields.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Now, this is-- this brings me to an interesting point.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I also went out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "First of all, you went out in the fresh air.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
